{"image_id": "PPL_2009_page_60", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "40", "bbox": [593.5, 1548.3, 619.7, 1571.4]}, {"text": "(a) Reflects principal maturities only based on legal maturity dates.  See Note 7 to", "bbox": [41.3, 80.6, 599.7, 99.0]}, {"text": "the Financial Statements for a discussion of the remarketing feature related to", "bbox": [71.5, 99.7, 592.8, 118.1]}, {"text": "PPL Energy Supply's 5.70% REset Put Securities, as well as discussion of", "bbox": [71.5, 118.8, 570.2, 137.2]}, {"text": "variable-rate remarketable bonds issued by the PEDFA on behalf of PPL", "bbox": [71.5, 138.1, 561.1, 156.5]}, {"text": "Energy Supply and PPL Electric.  PPL does not have any significant capital", "bbox": [71.5, 157.2, 580.8, 175.6]}, {"text": "lease obligations.", "bbox": [71.5, 176.3, 191.4, 194.8]}, {"text": "(b) Assumes interest payments through maturity.  The payments herein are subject", "bbox": [41.3, 195.6, 602.3, 214.0]}, {"text": "to change, as payments for debt that is or becomes variable-rate debt have been", "bbox": [71.5, 214.7, 604.5, 233.1]}, {"text": "estimated and payments denominated in British pounds sterling have been", "bbox": [71.5, 233.9, 570.7, 252.3]}, {"text": "translated to U.S. dollars at a current foreign currency exchange rate.", "bbox": [71.5, 253.1, 535.4, 271.5]}, {"text": "(c) The payments reflected herein are subject to change, as certain purchase", "bbox": [41.3, 272.2, 557.4, 290.6]}, {"text": "obligations included are estimates based on projected obligated quantities", "bbox": [71.5, 291.4, 566.5, 309.8]}, {"text": "and/or projected pricing under the contracts.  Purchase orders made in the", "bbox": [71.5, 310.5, 567.3, 328.9]}, {"text": "ordinary course of business are excluded from the amounts presented.  The", "bbox": [71.5, 329.7, 576.0, 348.1]}, {"text": "payments also include obligations related to nuclear fuel and the installation of", "bbox": [71.5, 348.9, 601.1, 367.3]}, {"text": "the scrubbers, which are also reflected in the Capital Expenditures table", "bbox": [71.5, 368.0, 554.0, 386.4]}, {"text": "presented above.", "bbox": [71.5, 387.2, 187.8, 405.7]}, {"text": "(d) The amounts reflected represent WPD's contractual deficit pension funding", "bbox": [41.3, 406.4, 577.8, 424.8]}, {"text": "requirements arising from an actuarial valuation performed in March 2007.", "bbox": [71.5, 425.5, 580.9, 443.9]}, {"text": "The U.K. electricity regulator currently allows a recovery of a substantial", "bbox": [71.5, 444.8, 564.5, 463.2]}, {"text": "portion of the contributions relating to the plan deficit; however, WPD cannot", "bbox": [71.5, 463.9, 595.2, 482.3]}, {"text": "be certain that this will continue beyond the current and next review periods,", "bbox": [71.5, 483.0, 587.3, 501.4]}, {"text": "which extend to March 31, 2015.  Based on the current funded status of PPL's", "bbox": [71.5, 502.3, 595.5, 520.7]}, {"text": "U.S. qualified pension plans, no cash contributions are required.  See Note 12", "bbox": [71.5, 521.4, 593.5, 539.8]}, {"text": "to the Financial Statements for a discussion of expected contributions.", "bbox": [71.5, 540.5, 543.4, 558.9]}, {"text": "(e) At December 31, 2009, total unrecognized tax benefits of $212 million were", "bbox": [41.3, 559.8, 585.3, 578.2]}, {"text": "excluded from this table as PPL cannot reasonably estimate the amount and", "bbox": [71.5, 578.9, 580.1, 597.3]}, {"text": "period of future payments.  See Note 5 to the Financial Statements for", "bbox": [71.5, 598.0, 542.6, 616.4]}, {"text": "additional information.", "bbox": [71.5, 617.3, 229.5, 635.7]}, {"text": "Dividends", "bbox": [41.3, 660.7, 131.2, 683.9]}, {"text": "PPL views dividends as an integral component of shareowner", "bbox": [41.3, 708.6, 560.6, 731.8]}, {"text": "return and expects to continue to pay dividends in amounts that", "bbox": [41.3, 732.7, 574.3, 755.8]}, {"text": "are within the context of maintaining a capitalization structure", "bbox": [41.3, 756.5, 565.2, 779.7]}, {"text": "that supports investment grade credit ratings.  In 2009, PPL", "bbox": [41.3, 780.6, 542.4, 803.7]}, {"text": "increased the annualized dividend rate on its common stock from", "bbox": [41.3, 804.4, 590.0, 827.6]}, {"text": "$1.34 to $1.38 per share, effective with the April 1, 2009", "bbox": [41.3, 828.5, 521.3, 851.6]}, {"text": "dividend payment.  Future dividends will be declared at the", "bbox": [41.3, 852.5, 542.0, 875.6]}, {"text": "discretion of the Board of Directors and will depend upon", "bbox": [41.3, 876.4, 528.7, 899.5]}, {"text": "available earnings, cash flows, financial requirements and other", "bbox": [41.3, 900.4, 577.4, 923.5]}, {"text": "relevant factors at the time.  As discussed in Note 7 to the", "bbox": [41.3, 924.4, 527.6, 947.5]}, {"text": "Financial Statements, PPL may not declare or pay any cash", "bbox": [41.3, 948.3, 540.8, 971.4]}, {"text": "dividend on its common stock during any period in which PPL", "bbox": [41.3, 972.3, 569.9, 995.4]}, {"text": "Capital Funding defers interest payments on its 2007 Series A", "bbox": [41.3, 996.3, 563.5, 1019.4]}, {"text": "Junior Subordinated Notes due 2067.  No such deferrals have", "bbox": [41.3, 1020.2, 558.2, 1043.3]}, {"text": "occurred or are currently anticipated.", "bbox": [41.3, 1044.2, 355.4, 1067.3]}, {"text": "PPL Electric expects to continue to pay quarterly dividends on", "bbox": [41.3, 1092.1, 568.2, 1115.2]}, {"text": "its outstanding preferred securities, if and as declared by its", "bbox": [41.3, 1116.1, 541.8, 1139.2]}, {"text": "Board of Directors.", "bbox": [41.3, 1140.1, 208.2, 1163.2]}, {"text": "See Note 7 to the Financial Statements for other restrictions", "bbox": [41.3, 1188.0, 545.0, 1211.2]}, {"text": "related to distributions on capital interests for PPL subsidiaries.", "bbox": [41.3, 1212.0, 575.1, 1235.2]}, {"text": "Purchase or Redemption of Debt Securities", "bbox": [41.3, 1260.0, 408.1, 1283.1]}, {"text": "PPL will continue to evaluate purchasing or redeeming", "bbox": [41.3, 1312.4, 505.5, 1335.5]}, {"text": "outstanding debt securities and may decide to take action", "bbox": [41.3, 1336.4, 522.5, 1359.6]}, {"text": "depending upon prevailing market conditions and available cash.", "bbox": [41.3, 1360.5, 598.8, 1383.6]}, {"text": "Credit Ratings", "bbox": [622.7, 80.6, 760.7, 104.0]}, {"text": "Moody's, S&P and Fitch periodically review the credit ratings on", "bbox": [622.8, 128.7, 1171.1, 151.8]}, {"text": "the debt and preferred securities of PPL and its subsidiaries.", "bbox": [622.8, 152.7, 1133.2, 175.8]}, {"text": "Based on their respective independent reviews, the rating", "bbox": [622.8, 176.6, 1104.8, 199.7]}, {"text": "agencies may make certain ratings revisions or ratings", "bbox": [622.8, 200.6, 1080.0, 223.7]}, {"text": "affirmations.", "bbox": [622.8, 224.6, 735.2, 247.7]}, {"text": "A credit rating reflects an assessment by the rating agency of the", "bbox": [622.8, 272.5, 1167.0, 295.6]}, {"text": "creditworthiness associated with an issuer and particular", "bbox": [622.8, 296.5, 1098.0, 319.7]}, {"text": "securities that it issues.  The credit ratings of PPL and its", "bbox": [622.8, 320.4, 1101.6, 343.6]}, {"text": "subsidiaries are based on information provided by PPL and other", "bbox": [622.8, 344.4, 1169.3, 367.6]}, {"text": "sources.  The ratings of Moody's, S&P and Fitch are not a", "bbox": [622.8, 368.3, 1110.7, 391.5]}, {"text": "recommendation to buy, sell or hold any securities of PPL or its", "bbox": [622.8, 392.4, 1160.5, 415.5]}, {"text": "subsidiaries.  Such ratings may be subject to revisions or", "bbox": [622.8, 416.4, 1100.4, 439.5]}, {"text": "withdrawal by the agencies at any time and should be evaluated", "bbox": [622.8, 440.3, 1159.4, 463.4]}, {"text": "independently of each other and any other rating that may be", "bbox": [622.8, 464.3, 1134.9, 487.4]}, {"text": "assigned to the securities.  A downgrade in PPL's or its", "bbox": [622.8, 488.3, 1086.0, 511.4]}, {"text": "subsidiaries' credit ratings could result in higher borrowing costs", "bbox": [622.8, 512.2, 1166.5, 535.3]}, {"text": "and reduced access to capital markets.", "bbox": [622.8, 536.2, 946.3, 559.3]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the credit ratings of PPL and its", "bbox": [622.8, 584.1, 1166.5, 607.2]}, {"text": "rated subsidiaries at December 31, 2009:", "bbox": [622.8, 608.1, 968.6, 631.2]}, {"text": "Moody's", "bbox": [878.1, 656.0, 943.5, 674.4]}, {"text": "S&P", "bbox": [1004.6, 656.0, 1042.1, 674.4]}, {"text": "Fitch (a)", "bbox": [1099.3, 655.6, 1163.1, 674.0]}, {"text": "PPL", "bbox": [622.8, 676.3, 658.3, 694.7]}, {"text": "Issuer Rating", "bbox": [646.1, 695.0, 738.8, 713.4]}, {"text": "Baa2", "bbox": [891.7, 695.0, 930.1, 713.4]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1004.8, 695.0, 1042.3, 713.4]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1112.5, 695.0, 1150.0, 713.4]}, {"text": "Outlook", "bbox": [646.1, 714.3, 705.0, 732.7]}, {"text": "Negative", "bbox": [878.7, 714.3, 943.0, 732.7]}, {"text": "Negative", "bbox": [991.3, 714.3, 1055.7, 732.7]}, {"text": "STABLE", "bbox": [1097.8, 714.3, 1164.8, 732.7]}, {"text": "PPL Capital Funding", "bbox": [624.3, 752.9, 781.2, 771.3]}, {"text": "Issuer Rating", "bbox": [646.1, 771.8, 738.8, 790.2]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1112.5, 771.8, 1150.0, 790.2]}, {"text": "Senior Unsecured Debt", "bbox": [646.1, 790.9, 806.0, 809.3]}, {"text": "Baa2", "bbox": [891.7, 790.9, 930.1, 809.3]}, {"text": "BBB-", "bbox": [1002.0, 790.9, 1045.1, 809.3]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1112.6, 790.9, 1150.1, 809.3]}, {"text": "Junior Subordinated Notes", "bbox": [646.1, 810.0, 828.1, 828.5]}, {"text": "Baa3", "bbox": [891.6, 810.0, 930.1, 828.5]}, {"text": "BB+", "bbox": [1005.6, 810.0, 1041.4, 828.5]}, {"text": "BBB-", "bbox": [1109.8, 810.0, 1152.8, 828.5]}, {"text": "Outlook", "bbox": [646.1, 829.2, 705.0, 847.6]}, {"text": "Negative", "bbox": [878.7, 829.2, 943.1, 847.6]}, {"text": "STABLE", "bbox": [1097.7, 829.2, 1164.8, 847.6]}, {"text"